data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, corner lot brick ranch waiting for you to call it home. It is located in Kings Mountain's desirable Gold Run subdivision with NO HOA! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1985 sqft home features a spacious primary bedroom with ensuite, and French doors that lead to the huge deck. A large family room with a stone wall and fireplace, a kitchen center island with a gas cooktop with grill, and a wall oven with a built-in microwave. The laundry room features a built-in ironing board. French doors lead from the dining room to the deck, as well. Situated on 1.21 Acres with a lighted storage shed and an all-brick privacy fence to complete the outdoor living space.
